<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MusclePoints BETA</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/MusclePoints/logoMusclePoints.png" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-Gn5384xqQ1aoWXA+058RXPxPg6fy4IWvTNh0E263XmFcJlSAwiGgFAW/dAiS6JXm" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            border: none;
            outline: none !important;
        }
        body{
            background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #ffb14d, #fd07c9);
        }
        #navbar-container{
            
            height: 100px;
            margin: 10px 0 0 30px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .logo{
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgb(0, 0, 0);
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        
        

        #main-container{
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            flex-direction: row;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-around;
        }
        .text-glow{
            width: 360px;
            display: flex;
            margin-top: 100px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .text-glow>button{
           width: 240px;
           height: 70px;
           font-size: 20px;
           border-radius: 30px;
           background-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(to right, #fba405, #fd07c9);
           background-image: linear-gradient(to left, #fba405, #fd07c9);
           font-weight: bolder;
           margin-top: 20px;
           margin-bottom: 40px;
           
        }
        
        .glow {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px #fff, 0 0 20px #fff, 0 0 30px #ffffff, 0 0 40px #ffffff, 0 0 50px #ffffff, 0 0 60px #ffffff, 0 0 70px #ffffff;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        #carrousel-info{
            height: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            
        }
        #carrousel-itens{
            height: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            
        }
        .info-cards{
            background-color: white;
            width: 340px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            height: 300px;
            
            text-align: center;
            padding: 5px;
        }
        #infoCard1{
            background-image: url('/img/MusclePoints/linechart.png');
            background-size: 360px;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position-y: bottom;  
        }
        .info-cards p{
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .instrutorCard>p{
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        
        
        @media (max-width: 500px){
            .text-glow{
            width: 400px;
            
                }
            .glow {font-size: 50px;}
            .muscleLogoWB{
                width: 360px;
            }

            .info-cards{
                width: 500px;
                height: 400px;
            }
        #infoCard1{
            background-image: url('/img/MusclePoints/linechart.png');
            background-size: 500px;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position-y: bottom;  
        }
        .info-cards p{
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .instrutorCard>p{
            font-size: 23px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .instrutorImg{
            height: 250px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        }
        @media (min-width: 900px){
            
            .text-glow{
            width: 700px;
            
                }
            .glow {font-size: 70px;}
            .muscleLogoWB{
                width: 700px;
            }
            .text-glow{
            width: 400px;
            
                }
            .glow {font-size: 50px;}

            .info-cards{
                width: 800px;
                height: 400px;
            }
            .instrutorImg{
                height: 300px;
                margin-top: 40px;
            }
        #infoCard1{
            background-image: url('/img/MusclePoints/linechart.png');
            background-size: 700px;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-position-y: bottom;  
            font-size: 35px;
        }
        .info-cards p{
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .info-cards h2{
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .info-cards h1{
            font-size: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .instrutorCard>p{
            font-size: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        }
        

        
        
        
            
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div id="navbar-container">
        <img class="logo" src="/img/MusclePoints/mswaregLogo.jpg" alt="" height="90">
        <img src="/img/MusclePoints/crossedArrows.svg" alt="" height="50">
        <img class="logo" src="/img/MusclePoints/logoMusclePoints.png" alt="" height="90">

    </div>

    <div id="main-container">

        <div class="text-glow">
            <p class="glow">ACOMPANHE <br> SEUS RESULTADOS<br> DA MELHOR MANEIRA!</p>
            <button onclick="window.location.href = '/training'">VAMOS TREINAR!</button>
        </div>
        <div>
            <img class="muscleLogoWB" src="/img/MusclePoints/musclepointWithoutBackground.png" alt="">
        </div>

        <div id="carrousel-info">
            <div id="carouselExampleSlidesOnly" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" data-interval="4000">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                    <div class="carousel-item active">
                        <div id="infoCard1" class="info-cards">
                            <h1>Se desenvolva!</h1>
                            <p>Se desenvolva monitorando <br> seus próprios resultados, aqui <br> no <span style="color: orange;">MusclePoints</span></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-item">
                        <div class="info-cards">
                            <h2>Maximize seus resultados!</h2>
                            <div class="d-flex instrutorCard">
                                <img class="instrutorImg" src="/img/MusclePoints/instrutor.svg" alt="">
                                <p>Alcance seus objetivos de forma mais fácil e eficiente com a ajuda do seu personal trainer/instrutor e do
                                    <span style="color: orange;"></span>MusclePoints</span></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    
    
    


    
</body>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.12.9/dist/umd/popper.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js"
    integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl"
    crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

</html>